// 大板检测函数：检测货物名称/规格/备注中是否包含大板关键词和规格
function detectLargeSlab(cargoName: string, cargoSpec?: string, remarks?: string): {
  isLargeSlab: boolean;
  detectedKeywords: string[];
  detectedSpecs: string[];
} {
  const textToCheck = `${cargoName} ${cargoSpec || ''} ${remarks || ''}`;
  const keywords: string[] = [];
  const specs: string[] = [];

  // 检测关键词
  const keywordPatterns = [
    { pattern: /大板/g, label: "大板" },
    { pattern: /铁架/g, label: "铁架" },
    { pattern: /铁托/g, label: "铁托" },
    { pattern: /岩板/g, label: "岩板" },
  ];
  for (const { pattern, label } of keywordPatterns) {
    if (pattern.test(textToCheck)) {
      keywords.push(label);
    }
  }

  // 检测规格：1800×900及以上
  const sizeRegex = /(\d+)\s*[*×xX]\s*(\d+)/g;
  let match;
  while ((match = sizeRegex.exec(textToCheck)) !== null) {
    const w = parseInt(match[1]);
    const h = parseInt(match[2]);
    if ((w >= 1800 && h >= 900) || (h >= 1800 && w >= 900)) {
      specs.push(`${match[1]}×${match[2]}`);
    }
  }

  // 有大板相关关键词或大规格尺寸
  const isLargeSlab = keywords.length > 0 || specs.length > 0;
  return { isLargeSlab, detectedKeywords: keywords, detectedSpecs: specs };
}

type ParsedOrder = {
  _uid: string; // 唯一标识，防止删除行时数据串位
  customerName: string;
  warehouseName: string;
  orderNumber: string;
  mergedPlanNumber: string;
  customerPrice: string;
  cargoName: string;
  weight: string;
  originCity: string;
  destinationCity: string;
  deliveryAddress: string;
  receiverName: string;
  receiverPhone: string;
  shippingNote: string;
  remarks: string;
  isUrgent: boolean;
  urgentReason: string;
  isLargeSlab: boolean;
  chargeableWeight: string;
  packageCount: string;
  confidence: Record<string, "high" | "medium" | "low">;
};

let _uidCounter = 0;
function genUid(): string {
  return `uid-${Date.now()}-${++_uidCounter}-${Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 8)}`;
}

export default function OrderCreate() {
  const [location, setLocation] = useLocation();
  const utils = trpc.useUtils();
  const ltlSubchainPrefill = useMemo(
    () => parseLtlSubchainSearch(typeof window !== "undefined" ? window.location.search : ""),
    [location],
  );
  const returnPath = ltlSubchainPrefill?.returnPath || "/station/entry";
  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState(ltlSubchainPrefill ? "manual" : "smart-paste");

  // ===== 手动录入 =====
  const { data: customers } = trpc.customer.list.useQuery({ activeOnly: true });
  const { data: warehouses } = trpc.warehouse.list.useQuery({ activeOnly: true });

  const [form, setForm] = useState({
    businessType: "outsource" as "outsource" | "self" | "ltl",
    isUrgent: false,
    urgentReason: "",
    customerId: undefined as number | undefined,
    customerName: "",
    customerPhone: "",
    settlementType: "monthly" as "monthly" | "cash" | "collect",
    cargoName: "",
    weight: "",
    packagingType: "pallet" as "pallet" | "loose" | "pallet_loaded",
    cargoSpec: "",
    specialRequirements: "",
    warehouseId: undefined as number | undefined,
    warehouseName: "",
    originCity: "",
    deliveryAddress: "",
    destinationCity: "",
    receiverName: "",
    receiverPhone: "",
    quotedPrice: "",
    orderNumber: "",
    mergedPlanNumber: "",
    customerPrice: "",
    shippingNote: "",
    remarks: "",
    department: "",
    // 大板相关字段
    isLargeSlab: false,
    chargeableWeight: "",
    packageCount: undefined as number | undefined,
  });

  // 大板强制确认弹窗
  const [largeSlabDialog, setLargeSlabDialog] = useState(false);
  const [largeSlabDetection, setLargeSlabDetection] = useState<{
    keywords: string[];
    specs: string[];
  }>({ keywords: [], specs: [] });
  const [pendingSubmit, setPendingSubmit] = useState(false);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (!ltlSubchainPrefill) return;
    setActiveTab("manual");
    setForm((prev) => ({
      ...prev,
      ...ltlSubchainPrefill.defaults,
      customerId: prev.customerId,
      warehouseId: prev.warehouseId,
      packagingType: prev.packagingType,
      quotedPrice: prev.quotedPrice,
      customerPrice: prev.customerPrice,
      cargoSpec: prev.cargoSpec,
      specialRequirements: prev.specialRequirements,
      warehouseName: prev.warehouseName,
      isUrgent: prev.isUrgent,
      urgentReason: prev.urgentReason,
      isLargeSlab: prev.isLargeSlab,
      chargeableWeight: prev.chargeableWeight,
      packageCount: prev.packageCount,
    }));
  }, [ltlSubchainPrefill]);

  const updateStatusMutation = trpc.order.updateStatus.useMutation();
  const createMutation = trpc.order.create.useMutation({
    onSuccess: async (data) => {
      utils.order.list.invalidate();
      utils.order.stats.invalidate();
      if (ltlSubchainPrefill) {
        try {
          await updateStatusMutation.mutateAsync({ id: data.id, status: "pending_price" });
          toast.success(`已创建${ltlSubchainPrefill.stageLabel}，并转入外请待定价队列：${data.orderNumber}`);
          setLocation(returnPath);
          return;
        } catch (err: any) {
          toast.error(`子链已创建，但转入待定价失败：${err?.message || "请手动处理"}`);
          setLocation(returnPath);
          return;
        }
      }
      toast.success(`订单已进入录单台待分流队列！订单号：${data.orderNumber}`);
      setLocation("/station/entry");
    },
    onError: (err) => {
      toast.error(`创建失败：${err.message}`);
    },
  });

  const handleCustomerChange = (customerId: string) => {
    const id = parseInt(customerId);
    const customer = customers?.find((c) => c.id === id);
    if (customer) {
      setForm((prev) => ({
        ...prev,
        customerId: id,
        customerName: customer.name,
        customerPhone: customer.phone || "",
        settlementType: (customer.settlementType as any) || "monthly",
        department: customer.department || "",
      }));
    }
  };

  const handleWarehouseChange = (warehouseId: string) => {
    const id = parseInt(warehouseId);
    const warehouse = warehouses?.find((w) => w.id === id);
    if (warehouse) {
      setForm((prev) => ({
        ...prev,
        warehouseId: id,
        warehouseName: warehouse.name,
        originCity: warehouse.city || "",
      }));
    }
  };

  // 实际提交逻辑
  const doSubmit = useCallback((formData: typeof form) => {
    createMutation.mutate({
      ...formData,
      orderNumber: formData.orderNumber.trim(),
      mergedPlanNumber: formData.mergedPlanNumber || undefined,
      customerId: formData.customerId,
      warehouseId: formData.warehouseId,
      weight: formData.weight || undefined,
      customerPrice: formData.customerPrice || undefined,
      quotedPrice: formData.quotedPrice || undefined,
      department: formData.department || undefined,
      urgentReason: formData.urgentReason || undefined,
      cargoSpec: formData.cargoSpec || undefined,
      specialRequirements: formData.specialRequirements || undefined,
      deliveryAddress: formData.deliveryAddress || undefined,
      receiverName: formData.receiverName || undefined,
      receiverPhone: formData.receiverPhone || undefined,
      shippingNote: formData.shippingNote || undefined,
      remarks: formData.remarks || undefined,
      isLargeSlab: formData.isLargeSlab || undefined,
      chargeableWeight: formData.chargeableWeight || undefined,
      packageCount: formData.packageCount || undefined,
      parentId: ltlSubchainPrefill?.parentId,
      parentIds: ltlSubchainPrefill?.parentIds,
      subchainStage: ltlSubchainPrefill?.stage,
    });
  }, [createMutation, ltlSubchainPrefill]);

  // 表单验证错误字段高亮
  const [formErrors, setFormErrors] = useState<Record<string, string>>({});

  const handleSubmit = () => {
    const errors: Record<string, string> = {};
    if (!form.orderNumber.trim()) errors.orderNumber = "请填写客户订单号";
    if (!form.customerName) errors.customerName = "请选择客户";
    if (!form.destinationCity) errors.destinationCity = "请填写目的城市";
    if (!form.cargoName) errors.cargoName = "请填写货物名称";
    if (form.weight && (isNaN(parseFloat(form.weight)) || parseFloat(form.weight) < 0)) {
      errors.weight = "重量不能为负数";
    }
    if (form.customerPrice && (isNaN(parseFloat(form.customerPrice)) || parseFloat(form.customerPrice) < 0)) {
      errors.customerPrice = "客户报价不能为负数";
    }

    if (Object.keys(errors).length > 0) {
      setFormErrors(errors);
      const firstError = Object.values(errors)[0];
      toast.error(firstError);
      return;
    }
    setFormErrors({});

    // 大板检测
    const detection = detectLargeSlab(form.cargoName, form.cargoSpec, form.remarks);
    if (detection.isLargeSlab && !form.isLargeSlab) {
      // 检测到大板但用户未标记，弹出强制确认
      setLargeSlabDetection({
        keywords: detection.detectedKeywords,
        specs: detection.detectedSpecs,
      });
      setLargeSlabDialog(true);
      setPendingSubmit(true);
      return;
    }

    // 大板必填字段校验
    if (form.isLargeSlab) {
      if (form.businessType !== "ltl" && !form.chargeableWeight) {
        toast.error("大板整车订单必须填写计费重量（客户给的包车重量）");
        return;
      }
      if (form.businessType === "ltl" && !form.packageCount) {
        toast.error("大板零担订单必须填写架数");
        return;
      }
    }

    doSubmit(form);
  };

  // 大板确认弹窗：确认是大板
  const handleConfirmLargeSlab = () => {
    setForm((prev) => ({ ...prev, isLargeSlab: true }));
    setLargeSlabDialog(false);
    // 不自动提交，让用户填写大板必填字段
    toast.info("已标记为大板订单，请填写计费重量或架数后再提交");
  };

  // 大板确认弹窗：确认不是大板
  const handleDenyLargeSlab = () => {
    setLargeSlabDialog(false);
    if (pendingSubmit) {
      setPendingSubmit(false);
      doSubmit({ ...form, isLargeSlab: false });
    }
  };

  // ===== 智能粘贴 =====
  const [rawText, setRawText] = useState("");
  const [parsedOrders, setParsedOrders] = useState<ParsedOrder[]>([]);
  const [parentRemarks, setParentRemarks] = useState("");
  const [businessTypes, setBusinessTypes] = useState<string[]>([]);
  const [isParsing, setIsParsing] = useState(false);
  const [isSubmitting, setIsSubmitting] = useState(false);
  const [submitted, setSubmitted] = useState(false);
  const [expandedPlans, setExpandedPlans] = useState<Set<string>>(new Set());
  const [urgentConfirmOpen, setUrgentConfirmOpen] = useState(false);
  const [pendingRemoveUid, setPendingRemoveUid] = useState<string | null>(null);

  // 按合并计划号分组（用于预览表格的整组显示）
  const parsedGroups = useMemo(() => {
    if (parsedOrders.length === 0) return [];
    return groupOrdersByPlan(parsedOrders.map((o, i) => ({ ...o, _idx: i })));
  }, [parsedOrders]);

  const togglePlanExpand = (planNumber: string) => {
    setExpandedPlans(prev => {
      const next = new Set(prev);
      if (next.has(planNumber)) next.delete(planNumber);
      else next.add(planNumber);
      return next;
    });
  };

  // 整组设置业务类型
  const setGroupBusinessType = (planNumber: string, type: string) => {
    setBusinessTypes(prev => {
      const updated = [...prev];
      parsedOrders.forEach((o, i) => {
        if (o.mergedPlanNumber === planNumber) updated[i] = type;
      });
      return updated;
    });
  };

  const parseMutation = trpc.smartPaste.parse.useMutation({
    onSuccess: (data) => {
      const orders = (data.orders || []).map((o: any) => ({ ...o, _uid: genUid() }));
      setParsedOrders(orders);
      setParentRemarks((data.parentRemarks || "").trim());
      setBusinessTypes(orders.map(() => "outsource"));
      if (orders.length === 0) {
        toast.warning("未能从文本中识别出订单信息，请检查输入内容");
      } else {
        // 检测每条订单是否有大板（优先使用LLM返回的isLargeSlab，再用前端detectLargeSlab补充检测shippingNote）
        let largeSlabCount = 0;
        for (const order of orders) {
          if (order.isLargeSlab) {
            largeSlabCount++;
          } else {
            const det = detectLargeSlab(order.cargoName, order.shippingNote || '', order.remarks);
            if (det.isLargeSlab) {
              (order as any).isLargeSlab = true;
              largeSlabCount++;
            }
          }
        }
        if (largeSlabCount > 0) {
          toast.info(`检测到 ${largeSlabCount} 条可能为大板订单，已自动标记，请确认`);
        }
        toast.success(`成功识别 ${orders.length} 条订单`);
      }
      setIsParsing(false);
    },
    onError: (err) => {
      toast.error(`解析失败：${err.message}`);
      setIsParsing(false);
    },
  });

  const batchCreateMutation = trpc.order.batchCreate.useMutation();

  const handleParse = () => {
    if (!rawText.trim()) {
      toast.error("请先粘贴文本内容");
      return;
    }
    setIsParsing(true);
    setParsedOrders([]);
    setParentRemarks("");
    setSubmitted(false);
    parseMutation.mutate({ text: rawText });
  };

  const handleFieldEdit = (idx: number, field: string, value: string | boolean) => {
    setParsedOrders((prev) => {
      const updated = [...prev];
      (updated[idx] as any)[field] = value;
      return updated;
    });
  };

  const handleRemoveOrder = (uid: string) => {
    setParsedOrders((prev) => {
      const removeIdx = prev.findIndex(o => o._uid === uid);
      if (removeIdx === -1) return prev;
      setBusinessTypes((bt) => bt.filter((_, i) => i !== removeIdx));
      return prev.filter(o => o._uid !== uid);
    });
    setPendingRemoveUid(null);
  };

  // 点击提交按钮时，先做基本校验，再弹出加急确认弹窗
  const handleBatchSubmitClick = () => {
    if (parsedOrders.length === 0) return;
    // 客户和货物必填校验
    for (let i = 0; i < parsedOrders.length; i++) {
      const order = parsedOrders[i];
      if (!order.customerName?.trim()) {
        toast.error(`第 ${i + 1} 条订单缺少客户名称，请填写后再提交`);
        return;
      }
      if (!order.cargoName?.trim()) {
        toast.error(`第 ${i + 1} 条订单缺少货物名称，请填写后再提交`);
        return;
      }
      if (order.isUrgent && !order.urgentReason?.trim()) {
        toast.error(`第 ${i + 1} 条订单标记为加急但未填写加急理由，请填写后再提交`);
        return;
      }
    }
    // 弹出加急确认弹窗，强制客服确认是否有加急订单
    setUrgentConfirmOpen(true);
  };

  // 确认后真正执行提交（一次网络请求批量插入）
  const handleBatchSubmit = async () => {
    if (parsedOrders.length === 0) return;
    setIsSubmitting(true);

    // 构建批量提交数据
    const batchData = parsedOrders.map((order, i) => {
      const bt = businessTypes[i] || "outsource";
      const custName = (order.customerName || "").trim();
      const matchedCustomer = custName ? customers?.find(
        (c) => c.name === custName || c.name.includes(custName) || custName.includes(c.name)
      ) : undefined;
      const det = order.isLargeSlab
        ? { isLargeSlab: true }
        : detectLargeSlab(order.cargoName, order.shippingNote || '', order.remarks);

      return {
        businessType: bt as "outsource" | "self" | "ltl",
        isUrgent: order.isUrgent,
        urgentReason: order.urgentReason || undefined,
        customerId: matchedCustomer?.id,
        customerName: custName || matchedCustomer?.name || undefined,
        customerPhone: order.receiverPhone || undefined,
        cargoName: order.cargoName || undefined,
        weight: order.weight ? parseFloat(order.weight).toFixed(3) : undefined,
        originCity: order.originCity || undefined,
        destinationCity: order.destinationCity || undefined,
        deliveryAddress: order.deliveryAddress || undefined,
        receiverName: order.receiverName || undefined,
        receiverPhone: order.receiverPhone || undefined,
        orderNumber: order.orderNumber || `AUTO-${Date.now()}-${i}`,
        mergedPlanNumber: order.mergedPlanNumber || undefined,
        customerPrice: order.customerPrice || undefined,
        shippingNote: order.shippingNote || undefined,
        remarks: order.remarks || undefined,
        warehouseName: order.warehouseName || undefined,
        isLargeSlab: det.isLargeSlab || undefined,
        chargeableWeight: order.chargeableWeight || undefined,
        packageCount: order.packageCount ? parseInt(order.packageCount) : undefined,
      };
    });

    try {
      const result = await batchCreateMutation.mutateAsync({ orders: batchData });
      setSubmitted(true);
      utils.order.list.invalidate();
      utils.order.stats.invalidate();
      toast.success(`全部 ${result.count} 条订单已进入录单台待分流队列！`);
    } catch (err: any) {
      toast.error(`批量创建失败：${err.message}`);
    } finally {
      setIsSubmitting(false);
    }
  };

  return (
    <DashboardLayout>
      <div className="space-y-4 max-w-6xl">
        {/* 头部 */}
        <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
            <Button variant="ghost" size="sm" onClick={() => setLocation(returnPath)}>
              <ArrowLeft className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
              {ltlSubchainPrefill ? `返回${ltlSubchainPrefill.stageLabel}来源页` : "返回录单台"}
            </Button>
            <div>
              <h1 className="text-xl font-semibold">{ltlSubchainPrefill ? `新建${ltlSubchainPrefill.stageLabel}` : "新建订单"}</h1>
              <p className="mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                {ltlSubchainPrefill
                  ? `${ltlSubchainPrefill.helperText} 来源主单：${ltlSubchainPrefill.sourceLabel}。`
                  : "订单提交后会先进入录单台“待分流”队列，再由录单台分流到外请、自运或零担。"}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          {activeTab === "manual" && (
            <Button onClick={handleSubmit} disabled={createMutation.isPending}>
              {createMutation.isPending ? (
                <Loader2 className="h-4 w-4 mr-1 animate-spin" />
              ) : (
                <Save className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
              )}
              {ltlSubchainPrefill ? "提交并进入外请待定价" : "提交并进入待分流"}
            </Button>
          )}
        </div>

        {ltlSubchainPrefill && (
          <Card className="border-cyan-200 bg-cyan-50/70">
            <CardContent className="flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 text-sm text-cyan-900">
              <div className="flex items-start gap-3">
                <Route className="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 text-cyan-700" />
                <div className="space-y-1">
                  <div className="font-medium">{ltlSubchainPrefill.stageLabel}来源主单：{ltlSubchainPrefill.sourceLabel}</div>
                  <div className="text-xs leading-5 text-cyan-800">{ltlSubchainPrefill.queueHint}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div className="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs">
                <Badge variant="secondary" className="bg-white text-cyan-800 border border-cyan-200">来源主单：{ltlSubchainPrefill.sourceCount}单</Badge>
                <Badge variant="secondary" className="bg-white text-cyan-800 border border-cyan-200">主单号：{ltlSubchainPrefill.parentOrderNumber || "未提供"}</Badge>
                <Badge variant="secondary" className="bg-white text-cyan-800 border border-cyan-200">提交后流向：外请待定价</Badge>
                <Badge variant="secondary" className="bg-white text-cyan-800 border border-cyan-200">链路阶段：{ltlSubchainPrefill.stage === "pickup" ? "待询价前的提货段" : "主链发运后的配送段"}</Badge>
                {ltlSubchainPrefill.isCombinedLoad && (
                  <Badge variant="secondary" className="bg-white text-cyan-800 border border-cyan-200">合车外请：同车承接多单</Badge>
                )}
              </div>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        )}

